# Optional Post-related models
+------------------+       +------------------+
|       Post       |       |       Vote       |
+------------------+       +------------------+
| id (PK)          |       | id (PK)          |
| name             |       | user_id (FK)     |
| user_id (FK)     |       | post_id (FK)     |
| type             |       | type             |
| image/video/gif  |       +------------------+
| description      |
| is_spoiler       |       +------------------+
| censors          |       |     Comment      |
| created_at       |       +------------------+
| updated_at       |       | id (PK)          |
+------------------+       | user_id (FK)     |
                           | post_id (FK)     |
+------------------+       | likes            |
|  Post_Topic      |       | context          |
+------------------+       | created_at       |
| post_id (FK)     |       | updated_at       |
| topic_id (FK)    |       +------------------+
+------------------+

